{"tid":699530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特金會】中國外交部罕見發聲明： 願與各方繼續實現半島無核化","createTime":"2018-06-12T15:11:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T06:29:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":72,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"16944d15d3ac0f1b630f6c0f1e8b4a0905271f84","tid":699530,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180612/large/1528805760_b408.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180612%2Flarge%2F1528805760_b408.jpg&h=6c237fce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 中國外交部於晚上近8時罕見發出官方聲明，指朝美領導人會晤順利舉行，是推動朝鮮半島無核化和政治解決進程取得重要進展，中方對兩國領導人作出政治決斷表示高度讚賞。外交部重申堅持實現半島無核化，維護半島和平和穩定，並以通過對話協商解決問題。未來，中方繼續致力實現半島無核化和建立半島和平機制。<br />\n<br />\n【聲明全文】<br />\n<br />\n朝美領導人會晤順利舉行並取得了積極成果。這是推動朝鮮半島無核化和政治解決進程取得的重要進展。我們對朝美兩國領導人作出的政治決斷表示高度讚賞，對會晤取得的成果表示歡迎和支持，對有關各方為推動會晤取得成功所作努力予以積極評價。<br />\n<br />\n實現半島無核化，結束持續六十多年的敵視與對立，謀求半島和地區的持久和平與繁榮，符合時代發展潮流，也是國際社會的普遍呼聲。此次朝美領導人會晤及其取得的成果，是向着上述目標邁出的正確而重要的步伐。<br />\n<br />\n中方堅持實現半島無核化，堅持維護半島和平與穩定，堅持通過對話協商解決問題，為此作出了不懈努力。一段時間以來，半島形勢出現的重大積極變化，特別是朝美領導人會晤取得的成果，符合中方期待。我們希望並支持朝美雙方落實好兩國領導人達成的共識，推進後續協商，進一步鞏固和擴大成果，使政治解決半島問題成為可持續、不可逆的進程。<br />\n<br />\n中方作為半島近鄰和重要一方，願同有關各方一道，繼續致力於實現半島無核化和建立半島和平機制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58310501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58310501&d=JQD8j6zJUJvgyHEPV5JzaNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=09ac0c50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180612%2F58310501&h=8bfe14ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180612/58310501</a>"},{"pid":"dde3f35423f07874fdf42b43d1f92695e63317eb","tid":699530,"uid":48964,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:13:47.000Z","msg":"人地南韓都未出聲...好心啦天朝大國"},{"pid":"35eb757b6eca0ba279a741750ae2927b8b1fe483","tid":699530,"uid":36178,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:16:31.000Z","msg":"Trump：China did nothing"},{"pid":"adfaeca0719bf500fd6b468d0bf1cf85821fee64","tid":699530,"uid":90601,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:21:56.000Z","msg":"吳若希.jpg"},{"pid":"ed89707e3e95494d29b939d1cfe8fccbdbfd1e1a","tid":699530,"uid":27664,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"(邊個國家) : 企開啲啦，屌你老味"},{"pid":"c997784e98995d3fff70669f72c846bc80108d34","tid":699530,"uid":38316,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:25:49.000Z","msg":"中國嚟攞光環？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee46e718d8c5ecefc78bd995c0cf444d93a7fe1","tid":699530,"uid":2857,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/232717_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F232717_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=cb1cb609&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9cbbe8d7e12c1dc86b0ee7a6f289adc262416645","tid":699530,"uid":29295,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:28:27.000Z","msg":"繼續致力於實現半島無核化和<span style=\"color: red;\">建立半島和平機制</span><br />\n<br />\n笑死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家侵就係要踢走你呢個偽中立國 你仲ff可以有份建立人哋個機制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3271aee657e236fbc28aee1959fc250a8ed67dc8","tid":699530,"uid":31098,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:30:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice